        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What does an SEO service cost in Swansea?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most of our Swansea campaigns sit between £400 and £1,500 a month, depending on what you need. A single-location local campaign costs less than one covering Neath, Llanelli, and Carmarthen. We keep our pricing page up to date so you can see every tier before we chat." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How long before I start seeing results?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most Swansea businesses notice real ranking shifts within 3 to 6 months. Local wins — like showing up in the map pack around SA1 or Mumbles — can happen in as little as 4 to 8 weeks because competition here is lighter than Cardiff or Bristol." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Can you help my business show up on Google Maps?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "That's one of our favourite things to do. We sort out your Google Business Profile, tidy up citations, build review momentum, and make sure your name, address, and phone number match everywhere. The map pack is where the calls come from." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you do one-off SEO audits?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "We do. Our free audit covers technical health, keyword gaps, and local listing accuracy. If you want the deep dive, our paid audit adds competitor benchmarking, a full backlink check, and a prioritised action plan you can hand to any developer." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Why is SEO in Swansea different from bigger cities?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Swansea has its own search personality. Areas like Sketty, Uplands, and Morriston each attract different types of searches. Tourism queries spike around Gower and Mumbles in the summer. We shape every campaign around these local patterns instead of using a one-size-fits-all playbook." }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you optimise for AI search tools like ChatGPT and Perplexity?",
        "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. We structure your content so AI models can pick it up and cite your business in their answers. That means entity markup, topical authority signals, and the kind of formatting large language models prefer. It sits alongside traditional SEO — not instead of it." }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "name": "SEO Services in Swansea",
    "description": "Full-service search engine optimisation for Swansea businesses including local SEO, technical SEO, content strategy, link building, and AI search optimisation.",
    "provider": {
      "@type": "LocalBusiness",
      "name": "SEO Swansea",
      "url": "https://seoswansea.uk/",
      "sameAs": [],
      "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Swansea", "containedInPlace": { "@type": "Country", "name": "United Kingdom" } }
    },
    "areaServed": { "@type": "City", "name": "Swansea" },
    "serviceType": "Search Engine Optimisation",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "priceCurrency": "GBP",
      "price": "400",
      "priceSpecification": {
        "@type": "UnitPriceSpecification",
        "price": "400",
        "priceCurrency": "GBP",
        "unitText": "MONTH",
        "description": "Starting price for local SEO in Swansea"
      }
    }
  }
];
---
<Base title="SEO Services Swansea | Full-Service SEO | SEO Swansea" description="Friendly, full-service SEO in Swansea. Local search, technical fixes, content, link building, and AI search optimisation for businesses across SA1 and South Wales." schema={schema}>

  <nav class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <a href="/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">Home</a>
    <span class="mx-1">/</span>
    <span class="text-gray-700">Services</span>
  </nav>

  <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-brand mb-4">SEO Services in Swansea</h1>

  <div class="bg-rose-50 border-l-4 border-accent p-4 rounded-r-lg my-6">
    <p class="text-text/80 font-medium">We're a Swansea SEO team that helps local businesses get found online — through local search, technical fixes, content that actually ranks, honest link building, and AI search optimisation. We cover everything from SA1 Waterfront to Mumbles and right across South Wales. Every campaign starts with a proper look at your data and a straightforward growth plan. Sound good?</p>
  </div>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Good SEO connects your business with the people who are already looking for what you do. Maybe you're running a restaurant on Wind Street, a tech company at SA1 Waterfront, or a trade outfit near Swansea Enterprise Park. Whatever the case, the right approach puts you in front of local buyers at exactly the moment they need you. We build campaigns around Swansea's real commercial geography, seasonal search habits, and competitive landscape so every pound you spend actually moves the needle.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Our process is simple. We look at where you stand today, spot the gaps your competitors are using against you, fix the technical foundations, then build content and authority that Google rewards with better rankings. No jargon-stuffed reports that gather dust. No vanity numbers. Just more of the right visitors, more enquiries, and more revenue for your Swansea business.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Here's a rundown of every SEO service we offer, how each one plays out in the Swansea market, and what kind of results you can expect.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Local SEO for Swansea Businesses</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">For most businesses right here in Swansea, local SEO delivers the biggest bang for your buck. When someone types "plumber near me" or "best restaurant Swansea," Google pulls up its local pack and Maps results. If you're not showing up there, you're invisible to the people most ready to spend.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We work on every local signal Google pays attention to. That means your Google Business Profile, citations on directories like Yell, Thomson Local, and Bark, on-page location clues, and a solid review strategy. For businesses with more than one location, we create landing pages that target specific Swansea postcodes from SA1 right through to SA8.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Swansea's local search market breaks into distinct clusters. SA1 Waterfront pulls searches for tech services, coworking, and waterfront dining. Wind Street owns nightlife and hospitality queries. Swansea Enterprise Park picks up B2B and trade searches. We map your target keywords to these geographic pockets so your visibility matches where your customers are actually looking.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Our local SEO campaigns typically boost map pack rankings within 4 to 8 weeks. We track calls, direction requests, and website visits from your Google Business Profile so you can see the revenue impact in plain numbers. Have a look at our <a href="/areas/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">area coverage</a> to see the specific spots we target.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Technical SEO</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Technical SEO is the foundation everything else sits on. If your site's slow, hard for Google to crawl, or full of errors, no amount of content or links will fix things long-term. We sort out the technical problems that hold Swansea businesses back.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Our <a href="/technical-seo-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">technical SEO service</a> covers site speed, mobile responsiveness, crawl efficiency, indexation control, structured data, Core Web Vitals, HTTPS setup, and internal linking. We check every page using Screaming Frog, Google Search Console, and PageSpeed Insights, then hand you a prioritised fix list ranked by how much each one will actually move the dial.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Plenty of Swansea businesses run on WordPress or Shopify themes that ship with bloated code, render-blocking resources, and clunky mobile layouts. We strip out the slow bits without breaking your design. For ecommerce sites, we focus on faceted navigation, canonical tags, and product schema to stop the duplicate content headaches that plague online shops.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Technical SEO isn't a one-and-done job, either. Google tweaks its algorithm regularly, and your competitors keep changing things. We keep an eye on your technical health every month and fix problems before they cost you rankings.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Content Strategy</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Content is how Google works out what your business does and whether it deserves a top spot. A strong content plan builds topical authority around the subjects your customers care about, pulls in links naturally, and turns visitors into real enquiries.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We dig into the questions Swansea customers ask, the words they use, and the content gaps your competitors have left wide open. Then we put together a calendar that fills those gaps with pages built to rank and convert. Every piece targets a specific keyword group, links back to your service pages, and follows on-page SEO best practice from top to bottom.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">For Swansea businesses, locally relevant content packs a real punch. Guides to specific areas, industry tips, and useful local resources pull in search traffic and natural backlinks from local publishers, councils, and community groups. A well-written Gower Peninsula accommodation guide, for instance, can attract tourism-related links that lift your whole domain.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We handle the full content pipeline — keyword research, writing, optimisation, and publication. If you'd rather write things yourself, we give you detailed briefs with target keywords, word counts, heading structures, and internal linking guidance so you know exactly what to produce.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Link Building</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Backlinks are still one of Google's strongest ranking signals. A single quality link from a relevant, trusted website can shift your rankings more than months of on-page tweaks. Our link building service focuses on earning the kind of links Google actually values — from sources that matter to your industry and your patch.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We build links through digital PR, guest posts on industry publications, local business directories, partnerships with Swansea organisations, and content-driven outreach. We never buy links from dodgy link farms. Every link we earn comes from a real site with real readers and proper editorial standards.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">For businesses in and around Swansea, local link building works a treat. Links from Swansea Council, local news outlets like the South Wales Evening Post, Swansea University, Business Wales, and local chambers of commerce send strong geographic signals that push your local rankings up. We've built relationships with publishers across the South Wales region over the years.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Google Business Profile Optimisation</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Your Google Business Profile is often the very first thing potential customers see. It pops up in Maps, the local pack, and increasingly in AI-generated answers. A well-optimised profile drives calls, direction requests, website visits, and direct bookings — sometimes without the customer ever landing on your website.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We fine-tune every part of your GBP: business categories, service descriptions, attributes, photos, posts, Q&A, and review responses. We make sure your Name, Address, and Phone number match across every directory and citation source. For businesses covering multiple Swansea areas, we set up service area configurations so you show up in searches across Mumbles, Sketty, Morriston, Uplands, and beyond.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Reviews are a big deal here. We help you build a steady review pipeline, respond to feedback professionally, and handle any negative reviews constructively. Businesses with 20-plus reviews and a 4.5+ star rating consistently outperform the competition in the local pack.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">SEO Audits</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Every good SEO campaign starts with knowing where you stand. We offer two options: a <a href="/free-seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">free SEO audit</a> covering the essentials, and a thorough <a href="/seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">paid SEO audit</a> that gives you a full strategic roadmap.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">The free audit looks at your current Google rankings for your target keywords, your technical health score, how complete your Google Business Profile is, a quick comparison with your top competitors, and three priority things you can act on straight away. It takes 48 hours and comes with a 20-minute walkthrough call.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">The full audit goes much deeper. We look at your complete backlink profile, content gaps against your top five Swansea competitors, technical infrastructure, internal linking, conversion rates by landing page, and local citation accuracy. You get a prioritised 90-day plan with projected traffic and revenue impact for every recommendation.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">AI Search Optimisation</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">AI search tools like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, and Microsoft Copilot are changing how people find businesses. These tools pull together answers from across the web and cite their sources. If your business isn't set up as something they can reference, you're missing out on a growing stream of high-intent traffic.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Our <a href="/ai-search-optimisation-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">AI search optimisation service</a> positions your Swansea business as a go-to source that AI models actually cite in their answers. We add entity markup, build topical authority, create content in the formats AI tools love to reference, and keep tabs on how you're showing up across AI search platforms.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">This isn't a replacement for traditional SEO — it's an extra layer that makes your existing rankings work harder. Businesses that pop up in both Google organic results and AI-generated answers grab a bigger share of clicks because they look authoritative across multiple channels.</p>

  <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-8">
    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Wondering how your Swansea business stacks up against the competition?</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="/free-seo-audit-swansea/" class="bg-accent text-brand px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent/80 font-semibold inline-block">Grab Your Free SEO Audit</a>
      <a href="/seo-pricing-swansea/" class="border border-accent text-accent px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent hover:text-brand inline-block font-semibold">View Pricing</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Why Swansea Businesses Work With Us</h2>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We're based right here in Swansea. We know the local market, the seasonal rhythms, the competition, and the commercial geography that shapes how people search in this part of Wales. That local knowledge feeds directly into sharper keyword targeting, more relevant content, and quicker results.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">We report on numbers that actually matter to your bottom line: rankings for the keywords that bring in money, organic traffic growth, enquiry volume, and cost per acquisition. We don't pad reports with impressions, bounce rates, or other feel-good metrics that look nice but don't pay the bills.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Every client gets a dedicated point of contact, monthly performance reviews, and direct access to the people doing the actual work. No account executives passing messages along. No outsourced deliverables. The person on your call is the same person building your links and writing your content.</p>

  <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Have a look at our <a href="/case-studies/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">case studies</a> to see what we've done for businesses across Swansea and South Wales. Browse our <a href="/industries/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">industry pages</a> to see how we tailor things for different sectors.</p>

  <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mt-12 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <div class="space-y-2 mb-8">
    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-text py-2 px-4">How much should I expect to pay for SEO in Swansea?</summary>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Most of our campaigns sit between £400 and £1,500 a month, depending on what's involved. A local-only campaign for a single-location business costs less than a regional push covering Neath, Llanelli, and Carmarthen. Check our <a href="/seo-pricing-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">pricing page</a> to see exactly what each tier includes before we have a chat.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-text py-2 px-4">When will I actually see a difference in my rankings?</summary>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Most Swansea businesses notice meaningful ranking improvements within 3 to 6 months. Local SEO wins — like popping up in the map pack around SA1 or Mumbles — can happen in 4 to 8 weeks because competition here tends to be lighter than in Cardiff or Bristol. Exactly how fast depends on where you're starting from, how competitive your keywords are, and the current state of your website.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-text py-2 px-4">What's the deal with Google Maps — can you get me in there?</summary>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Absolutely — it's one of the things we enjoy most. Google Business Profile optimisation sits at the heart of our local SEO service. We tidy up your listing, sort out reviews, build local citations, and make sure your NAP details are consistent across every directory. Most clients see map pack improvements within the first couple of months.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-text py-2 px-4">Can I just get an audit without signing up for a monthly contract?</summary>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Of course. Our <a href="/free-seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">free SEO audit</a> covers technical health, keyword gaps, and local listing accuracy. If you want something more detailed, our paid <a href="/seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">SEO audit</a> adds competitor benchmarking, a full action plan, and priority recommendations tailored to the Swansea market. No strings attached.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-text py-2 px-4">Do you work with AI search engines like ChatGPT and Perplexity?</summary>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Yes. Our <a href="/ai-search-optimisation-swansea/" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">AI search optimisation service</a> makes sure your content is structured so AI models can pick it up and cite you in their answers. We handle entity markup, authority signals, and source-citation formatting. It works hand-in-hand with traditional SEO to capture traffic from both conventional and AI-powered search.</p>
    </details>

    <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
      <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-text py-2 px-4">What makes SEO in Swansea different from bigger cities?</summary>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Swansea's got a search personality all its own. The population clusters in areas like Sketty, Uplands, and Morriston, each with different buying intent. Tourism searches spike seasonally around Gower Peninsula and Mumbles. Competition is lower than Cardiff, Bristol, or London, which means a focused campaign can deliver results faster than you might expect.</p>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-brand/5 border border-brand/20 rounded-lg p-6 my-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text mb-3">Ready to Grow Your Swansea Business?</h2>
    <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">Drop us a message to talk about your goals, look at how things stand today, and get a clear plan for what comes next.</p>
    <a href="/contact/" class="bg-accent text-brand px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent/80 font-semibold inline-block">Let's Chat</a>
  </div>

</Base>
